    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const body = $json.body || $json;\nconst sectionId = body.section_id\nconst input = body.input_json || {};\nconst context = body.plan_context || {};\nconst language = body.language || 'english';\nconst businessPlanId = body.business_plan_id;\n\nconst headings = language === 'french' ? `\n- Taille du marché\n- Segmentation du marché\n- Analyse concurrentielle\n- Analyse PESTEL\n- Analyse SWOT\n` : `\n- Market Size\n- Market Segmentation\n- Competitive Analysis\n- PESTEL Analysis\n- SWOT Analysis\n`;\n\nconst prompt = `\nYou are writing a professional business plan section: Market Analysis.\nLanguage: ${language}\n\n## Company Context\n${context.company_presentation || 'Not provided'}\n\n## Market Information\n- Target Market: ${input.target_market || 'Not provided'}\n- Market Size: ${input.market_size || 'Not provided'}\n- Target Customer: ${input.target_customer || 'Not provided'}\n- Competitors: ${input.competitors || 'Not provided'}\n- Market Trends: ${input.market_trends || 'Not provided'}\n- Demand Drivers: ${input.demand_drivers || 'Not provided'}\n- Supply Constraints: ${input.supply_constraints || 'Not provided'}\n\nWrite a detailed Market Analysis section. Include these headings:\n${headings}\n\nRules:\n- If a field says \"Not provided\", acknowledge it professionally\n- Do not invent fictional data\n- Minimum 400 words\n- Write in ${language}\nCRITICAL INSTRUCTION — OUTPUT FORMAT:\nYou MUST return your response in exactly this format. Any other format is invalid.\n\n=== SECTION_TEXT ===\n[Write your full detailed section here]\n=== MEMORY_SUMMARY ===\nMarket Size: [value]\nTarget Segment: [value]\nKey Competitors: [value]\nCompetitive Advantage: [value]\nTop Market Trend: [value]\nSWOT Summary: [value]\n`;\n\nreturn [{\n  json: {\n    prompt,\n    sectionId: sectionId,\n    business_plan_id: businessPlanId,\n    section_name: 'market_analysis',\n    language,\n    input_json: input,\n  }\n}];"
      },
